OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy and breezy start, with a
OL,6,Ffew outbreaks of rain. Perhaps the odd
OL,7,Fwarm sunnier spell developing early
OL,8,Fafternoon, along with isolated showers.
OL,9,
OL,10,CTonight:FAny rain or showers soon
OL,11,Fclearing into the evening with clear
OL,12,Fspells developing. Cloud then thickens
OL,13,Fagain from the west through the early
OL,14,Fhours of Thursday, but likely staying
OL,15,Fdry.
OL,16,
OL,17,CThursday:FSome warm sunny spells are
OL,18,Fexpected, but with cloud also building
OL,19,Fto bring occasional showers, heavy at
OL,20,Ftimes, Winds becoming light.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
