OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FOften
OL,6,Fcloudy Friday, with the odd shower,
OL,7,Fbut also some brighter spells. Rain
OL,8,Flikely Saturday morning, clearing to
OL,9,Fsunny spells and showers. Drier, and
OL,10,Fsunnier Sunday with winds easing.
